title: Urllib question. What happens when you save 2 images as the same file name?
author: t2_3yvtez7q

comments.author: krimpenrik
comments.body: Pretty easy to try out isn't it? Probably it's rewrite the first file

comments.author: Suhasbk98
comments.body: If it's the same file name with same extension, it will overwrite the first file data with new data.
